                            <i class="fas fa-star me-1"></i><i class="fas fa-star me-1"></i><i class="fas fa-star me-1"></i><i class="fas fa-star me-1"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-white-50 italic mb-4">"The mountain vistas from Chalet 101 were absolutely breathtaking. Having a private glowing pool surrounded by snow was a dream experience. Outstanding personal butler service."</p>
                        <div class="fw-bold text-white small">Lord Al-Maktoum</div>
                        <div class="text-warning" style="font-size: 0.75rem;">Stayed at Royal Pool Chalet</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="review-card">
                        <div class="d-flex text-warning mb-3">
                            <i class="fas fa-star me-1"></i><i class="fas fa-star me-1"></i><i class="fas fa-star me-1"></i><i class="fas fa-star me-1"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-white-50 italic mb-4">"The boutique suite fireplace created a remarkably cozy ambiance during our stay. Clean lines, premium linens, and a highly responsive support center. Will absolutely return."</p>
                        <div class="fw-bold text-white small">Lady Varela</div>
