                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="review-card">
                        <div class="d-flex text-warning mb-3">
                            <i class="fas fa-star me-1"></i><i class="fas fa-star me-1"></i><i class="fas fa-star me-1"></i><i class="fas fa-star me-1"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-white-50 italic mb-4">"Exceptional ocean view terrace! The infinity pool at sunset was a highlight. A truly premium booking engine that made securing the stay effortless. Stripe payment was smooth."</p>
